{"tid":1953133,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"拒強制關戲院卡拉OK　林鄭：相信商戶有足夠防疫","createTime":"2020-04-01T04:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T04:15:14.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df0240188c302b91d672ddfb8fcb37f57941724e","tid":1953133,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200211/_2020021115445038384.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200211%2F_2020021115445038384.jpeg&h=d0ab2100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前有打邊爐引發一家11人確診感染新冠病毒，行政會議成員林正財指會視乎疫情考慮關閉戲院等，食衛局長陳肇始昨亦強烈建議戲院及卡拉OK等多人聚集的場所暫時關閉。不過特首林鄭月娥今日就表示，不會強制要求有關娛樂場所暫停營業，相信各商戶已有措施確保顧客不受感染。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥呼籲市民盡量留在家中，減少親友聚會等社交活動，但香港是自由社會，不會強制娛樂場所關閉，相信商戶會確保有足夠防禦措施。有學者批評言論與行會成員口徑不一，斥林鄭不當機立斷關閉娛樂場所，罔顧港人性命安全。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她亦提到已向內地入境人士實施強制檢疫，跨境人流已減至最低，現在再談封關已經「無乜意思」。<br />\n<br />\n2020-02-11 15:40<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1698886/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%8B%92%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E9%97%9C%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E5%8D%A1%E6%8B%89ok-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E6%9C%89%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%A0%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1698886%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%258D%25A1%25E6%258B%2589ok-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=46061b06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1698886%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%258D%25A1%25E6%258B%2589ok-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB&h=19360434\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1698886/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%8B%92%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E9%97%9C%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E5%8D%A1%E6%8B%89ok-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E6%9C%89%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%A0%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB</a>"},{"pid":"9d7c727e16a71ad3405b9f9daa8c567dc7ea3390","tid":1953133,"uid":156130,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"但香港是自由社會，不會強制娛樂場所關閉，相信商戶會確保有足夠防禦措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁嘅時候就話政府有權乜乜乜，又話保障乜乜乜。<br />\n唔禁嘅時候就拎香港係自由社會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢唔覺矛盾㗎咩？"}]}